Attached are marked and clean versions of an updated draft of the Annex.  I 
have incorporated the concepts we discussed over the last few weeks and 
somewhat formalized in our meeting earlier this week.  I have also cleaned-up 
some of the language.

As you will note, there are a few blanks that need to be filled-in, including 
