basis upon which CL is designating business days.  I have also deleted the 
force majeure provision as we discussed since turning on and off the negative 
confirm function is not functionality the module currently has.  This will 
also require a modification to the force majeure provision of the ESA.

Please review the attached at your convenience and let me know your thoughts.

          


